QuestData.Title: Disciples of Naralex
QuestData.Description: $C, the Barrens used to be one of the most beautiful places in all of Kalimdor. It teemed with life and promise.$B$BNow, as you can see, that is no longer true. It is a land of great torment and strife.$B$BThe Disciples of Naralex seek to cleanse the Wailing Caverns and bring them back to their former beauty. Speak with Nalpak just inside the Wailing Caverns to help.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Nalpak in the Wailing Caverns.
